### ğŸŒ **1. Azure Account Basics**

| Concept                | Description                                                                   | Example                                                                                     |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Azure Account**      | Your personal or organizationâ€™s login to access Azure services.               | Your Microsoft account (e.g., [sai@outlook.com](mailto:sai@outlook.com)).                   |
| **Azure Subscription** | A billing container where Azure services (resources) are created and managed. | You may have separate subscriptions for **Development**, **Marketing**, and **Production**. |
| **Azure Resources**    | Actual services you create inside a subscription.                             | Virtual Machine, Database, Storage Account, etc.                                            |

