### ğŸ†“ **3. Azure Free Account vs Azure Student Account**

| Feature              | **Azure Free Account**        | **Azure Student Account**                         |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| Validity             | 12 months (Free tier)         | 12 months                                         |
| Credit               | $200 credit for 30 days       | $100 credit for 12 months                         |
| Always Free Services | 25+ products                  | 25+ products                                      |
| Developer Tools      | Not included by default       | Included (Visual Studio Code, GitHub tools, etc.) |
| Credit Card Required | âœ… Yes (for verification only) | âŒ No                                              |
| Ideal For            | Beginners / Professionals     | Students / Learners                               |

---

### âš™ï¸ **4. How to Create an Azure Account**

1. Go to **[azure.microsoft.com/free](https://azure.microsoft.com/free)**
2. Click **Start free**
3. Sign in using your **Microsoft** or **GitHub** account
4. Provide a **phone number** and **credit card (for verification only)**
5. Your **Free Account** and **First Subscription** are automatically created

